            "title": "Habitat Composition and Connectivity Predicts Bat Presence and Activity at Foraging Sites in a Large UK Conurbation",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "James D.",
                    "lastName": "Hale"
                },
                {
