            "title": "Thermoregulation during Flight: Body Temperature and Sensible Heat Transfer in Free-Ranging Brazilian Free-Tailed Bats (Tadarida brasiliensis)",
            "creators": [
                {
                    "creatorType": "author",
                    "firstName": "Jonathan D.",
